ls display a number of the\ndistinctive features of colloidal glasses and, strikingly, that their response\nto the flow conditions encountered during processing can be tuned by chemical\nadditives. These findings have implications for processing of dense CNC-polymer\ncomposites in solvent casting, 3D printing, and other manufacturing techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2019 16:08:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-15"}
