 might the pair of 1973 8-magnitude\noutbursts if there had been an earlier spin-down and spin-up cycle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2019 21:08:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
