antum potential, which helps understanding why the scale factor never\nvanishes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2019 02:49:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2019 13:26:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2019 21:48:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-07"}
