ial performance gain as compared to conceivable alternatives.\nThe results also suggest that increasing EV charging rate limit decreases\noverall cost almost linearly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2019 12:12:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-07"}
