Subsequently, we use testbed\nmeasurements and simulations to study the relationship between bot detection\ndelays and the sampling frequencies for device packets. Finally, we derive\ninsights from the obtained results and use them to design our proposed bot\ndetection algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2019 13:09:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 07:38:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 13:16:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-16"}
